name: complex_if_compare_common_left_lte
section: control-if-order
args: cond:Bool common:Int a:Int b:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Less-or-equal from a common left operand to an if expression must choose branchwise comparisons.
law: (= (fuzz-lte? {common} (if {cond} {a} {b})) (if {cond} (fuzz-lte? {common} {a}) (fuzz-lte? {common} {b})))
